{"tid":2154783,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［笑撚死］譚惠珠：民主派將會找到理由返回立法會","createTime":"2020-08-13T10:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T13:15:39.000Z","uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"88f25f3c1c7516aa1d8b322dda88d49087e00737","tid":2154783,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:24:48.000Z","msg":"基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠認為，反對派會找到理由返回議會，她並不擔心，但呼籲對方守法，包括港區國安法，不要拖政府後腿。<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠在本台節目《千禧年代》說，全國人大常委會決定第六屆立法會延任不少於1年，與基本法69條立法會任期4年一屆的條文，兩者並非矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，人大行使職責時要同時顧及基本法及中國憲法，憲法中有條文指出，全國人大可以決定特區的設立及其制度，不能想像超過1年並無立法會運作，認為人大行使職權是恰當。<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠說，特首引用緊急法延後選舉，並向中央提出要求處理的原因，只是因應疫情，並無提到議員就職及履職資格等問題，人大常委會於是討論立法會的補缺問題。<br />\n<br />\n她估計順延第六屆立法會繼續履職，是平穩過渡的最好方法，不用再舉行選舉，上一個立法年度的法案及預算不用由零開始，目前首要工作是令疫情壓下去，否則本港民生及經濟會停擺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543449-20200813.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543449-20200813.htm&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzgomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=6eb8dddc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543449-20200813.htm&h=a8c8e2ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543449-20200813.htm</a>"},{"pid":"55aa8c675e15e3ad1bc409c3673f33378d867505","tid":2154783,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:28:33.000Z","msg":"聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzgomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=d2520856\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok</a>"},{"pid":"8bef78f5be62a3e4ccc602b6eb47ef82e49461b0","tid":2154783,"uid":16320